'For installation on Node.js (NPM Package users), use the following shortcode:
npm install -g typescript

'To compile declare a function and use the shortcode:
tsc functioname.ts                    

'To run a web app use the following:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head><title>TypeScript functioname</title></head>
    <body>
        <script src="functioname.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
